<li role="presentation"><a href='?term="Clin%20Pharmacol%20Ther"[jour]' class="usa-link" role="menuitem" data-add-to-search="true">Add to search</a></li>
</ul></nav></section><section class="front-matter"><div class="ameta p font-secondary font-xs">
<hgroup><h1>Systems pharmacology augments drug safety surveillance</h1></hgroup><div class="cg p">
<a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Lorberbaum%20T"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id1"><span class="name western">Tal Lorberbaum</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id1">
